### Get all ornaments for authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/ornaments
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get specific ornament by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/ornaments/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get ornaments by aquarium ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/ornaments?aquariumId=1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Create decorative castle
POST {{baseUrl}}/ornaments
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Medieval Castle",
  "color": "Gray",
  "material": "Resin",
  "description": "Large decorative castle with multiple towers",
  "isAirPumpCompatible": true,
  "aquariumId": 1
}

